skdetail:

Invocation Name: soft white noise
des: Let this soft white noise lull you right to sleep! Soft white noise is at a slightly lower frequency than white noise and can help some people get extra relaxed as they go to bed. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Soft White Noise,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
